":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/06\/major-sin-insult-twice\/","url_meta":{"origin":32167,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Insults: Major sin to over-retaliate to provocation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among the worst of major sins, is to attack the reputation of a Muslim man without a just cause, and among the major sins is to revile twice in response to one insult.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14667,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/09\/false-oaths-suicide-cursing-takfir\/","url_meta":{"origin":32167,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sins: False oaths, suicide, cursing, excommunication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Thabit ibn al-Dahhak reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever swears falsely by a religion other than Islam, he is what he has professed. Whoever kills himself with something, he will be punished with it in the fire of Hell. Cursing a believer is like killing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\